{
  "video_id": "TS6lFDVR-3g",
  "title": "Why school should start later for teens | Wendy Troxel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Leslie Gauthier Reviewer: Joanna Pietrulewicz"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12180.0,
      "end_time": 14396.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s six o&#39;clock in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14420.0,
      "end_time": 15740.0,
      "text": "pitch black outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16460.0,
      "end_time": 19676.0,
      "text": "My 14-year-old son is fast asleep in his bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19700.0,
      "end_time": 22780.0,
      "text": "sleeping the reckless, deep sleep of a teenager."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23820.0,
      "end_time": 27796.0,
      "text": "I flip on the light and physically shake the poor boy awake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27820.0,
      "end_time": 30436.0,
      "text": "because I know that, like ripping off a Band-Aid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30460.0,
      "end_time": 32396.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s better to get it over with quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32420.0,
      "end_time": 34760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 38836.0,
      "text": "I have a friend who yells \"Fire!\" just to rouse her sleeping teen."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38860.0,
      "end_time": 40836.0,
      "text": "And another who got so fed up"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40860.0,
      "end_time": 43716.0,
      "text": "that she had to dump cold water on her son&#39;s head"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43740.0,
      "end_time": 45660.0,
      "text": "just to get him out of bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46420.0,
      "end_time": 48156.0,
      "text": "Sound brutal ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48180.0,
      "end_time": 49980.0,
      "text": "but perhaps familiar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51420.0,
      "end_time": 54276.0,
      "text": "Every morning I ask myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54300.0,
      "end_time": 55876.0,
      "text": "\"How can I --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55900.0,
      "end_time": 57635.0,
      "text": "knowing what I know"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57660.0,
      "end_time": 60750.0,
      "text": "and doing what I do for a living --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60100.0,
      "end_time": 62100.0,
      "text": "be doing this to my own son?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62860.0,
      "end_time": 64156.0,
      "text": "You see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64180.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65876.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a sleep researcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65900.0,
      "end_time": 68760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68100.0,
      "end_time": 69916.0,
      "text": "So I know far too much about sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69940.0,
      "end_time": 72636.0,
      "text": "and the consequences of sleep loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72660.0,
      "end_time": 76756.0,
      "text": "I know that I&#39;m depriving my son of the sleep he desperately needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76779.0,
      "end_time": 78660.0,
      "text": "as a rapidly growing teenager."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79180.0,
      "end_time": 81436.0,
      "text": "I also know that by waking him up"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81460.0,
      "end_time": 86116.0,
      "text": "hours before his natural biological clock tells him he&#39;s ready,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86140.0,
      "end_time": 88540.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m literally robbing him of his dreams --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89220.0,
      "end_time": 94996.0,
      "text": "the type of sleep most associated with learning, memory consolidation"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95200.0,
      "end_time": 96860.0,
      "text": "and emotional processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97580.0,
      "end_time": 100460.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just my kid that&#39;s being deprived of sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101580.0,
      "end_time": 105340.0,
      "text": "Sleep deprivation among American teenagers is an epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106180.0,
      "end_time": 110676.0,
      "text": "Only about one in 10 gets the eight to 10 hours of sleep per night"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110700.0,
      "end_time": 113900.0,
      "text": "recommended by sleep scientists and pediatricians."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115100.0,
      "end_time": 116836.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re thinking to yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116860.0,
      "end_time": 120116.0,
      "text": "\"Phew, we&#39;re doing good, my kid&#39;s getting eight hours,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120140.0,
      "end_time": 121356.0,
      "text": "remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121380.0,
      "end_time": 124875.0,
      "text": "eight hours is the minimum recommendation."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124900.0,
      "end_time": 126956.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re barely passing."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126980.0,
      "end_time": 129820.0,
      "text": "Eight hours is kind of like getting a C on your report card."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130780.0,
      "end_time": 133620.0,
      "text": "There are many factors contributing to this epidemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134420.0,
      "end_time": 138956.0,
      "text": "but a major factor preventing teens from getting the sleep they need"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138980.0,
      "end_time": 141298.0,
      "text": "is actually a matter of public policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141980.0,
      "end_time": 145859.0,
      "text": "Not hormones, social lives or Snapchat."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147340.0,
      "end_time": 148596.0,
      "text": "Across the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148620.0,
      "end_time": 153476.0,
      "text": "many schools are starting around 7:30am or earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153500.0,
      "end_time": 157596.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that major medical organizations recommend"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157620.0,
      "end_time": 162600.0,
      "text": "that middle and high school start no earlier than 8:30am."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163600.0,
      "end_time": 167196.0,
      "text": "These early start policies have a direct effect on how much --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167220.0,
      "end_time": 171220.0,
      "text": "or really how little sleep American teenagers are getting."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172340.0,
      "end_time": 176236.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re also pitting teenagers and their parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 180340.0,
      "text": "in a fundamentally unwinnable fight against their own bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181180.0,
      "end_time": 182996.0,
      "text": "Around the time of puberty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183200.0,
      "end_time": 186756.0,
      "text": "teenagers experience a delay in their biological clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186780.0,
      "end_time": 190460.0,
      "text": "which determines when we feel most awake and when we feel most sleepy."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191340.0,
      "end_time": 194980.0,
      "text": "This is driven in part by a shift in the release of the hormone melatonin."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195900.0,
      "end_time": 201436.0,
      "text": "Teenagers&#39; bodies wait to start releasing melatonin until around 11pm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201460.0,
      "end_time": 205780.0,
      "text": "which is two hours later than what we see in adults or younger children."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 207660.0,
      "end_time": 213676.0,
      "text": "This means that waking a teenager up at 6am is the biological equivalent"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213700.0,
      "end_time": 216660.0,
      "text": "of waking an adult up at 4am."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217580.0,
      "end_time": 221556.0,
      "text": "On the unfortunate days when I have to wake up at 4am,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 221580.0,
      "end_time": 222916.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a zombie."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222940.0,
      "end_time": 224676.0,
      "text": "Functionally useless."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224700.0,
      "end_time": 226316.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t think straight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226340.0,
      "end_time": 227836.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m irritable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227860.0,
      "end_time": 230300.0,
      "text": "and I probably shouldn&#39;t be driving a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231500.0,
      "end_time": 235620.0,
      "text": "But this is how many American teenagers feel every single school day."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 236100.0,
      "end_time": 239116.0,
      "text": "In fact, many of the, shall we say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239140.0,
      "end_time": 243476.0,
      "text": "unpleasant characteristics that we chalk up to being a teenager --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 243500.0,
      "end_time": 246916.0,
      "text": "moodiness, irritability, laziness, depression --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 246940.0,
      "end_time": 249820.0,
      "text": "could be a product of chronic sleep deprivation."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250900.0,
      "end_time": 253636.0,
      "text": "For many teens battling chronic sleep loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253660.0,
      "end_time": 259156.0,
      "text": "their go-to strategy to compensate is consuming large quantities of caffeine"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259180.0,
      "end_time": 261356.0,
      "text": "in the form of venti frappuccinos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261380.0,
      "end_time": 263219.0,
      "text": "or energy drinks and shots."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263900.0,
      "end_time": 265116.0,
      "text": "So essentially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 265140.0,
      "end_time": 271140.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got an entire population of tired but wired youth."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273420.0,
      "end_time": 277360.0,
      "text": "Advocates of sleep-friendly start times know"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 280596.0,
      "text": "that adolescence is a period of dramatic brain development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280620.0,
      "end_time": 282676.0,
      "text": "particularly in the parts of the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 282700.0,
      "end_time": 286236.0,
      "text": "that are responsible for those higher order thinking processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 290539.0,
      "text": "including reasoning, problem-solving and good judgment."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291140.0,
      "end_time": 294276.0,
      "text": "In other words, the very type of brain activity that&#39;s responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294300.0,
      "end_time": 298876.0,
      "text": "for reining in those impulsive and often risky behaviors"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298900.0,
      "end_time": 301835.0,
      "text": "that are so characteristic of adolescence"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 301860.0,
      "end_time": 305620.0,
      "text": "and that are so terrifying to us parents of teenagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 306420.0,
      "end_time": 308316.0,
      "text": "They know that like the rest of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 308340.0,
      "end_time": 310756.0,
      "text": "when teenagers don&#39;t get the sleep they need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310780.0,
      "end_time": 313916.0,
      "text": "their brains, their bodies and behaviors suffer"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313940.0,
      "end_time": 316580.0,
      "text": "with both immediate and lasting effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317100.0,
      "end_time": 318916.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t concentrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 318940.0,
      "end_time": 320836.0,
      "text": "their attention plummets"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 320860.0,
      "end_time": 324620.0,
      "text": "and many will even show behavioral signs that mimic ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 326140.0,
      "end_time": 330556.0,
      "text": "But the consequences of teen sleep loss go well beyond the classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 330580.0,
      "end_time": 334195.0,
      "text": "sadly contributing to many of the mental health problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334220.0,
      "end_time": 336916.0,
      "text": "that skyrocket during adolescence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 336940.0,
      "end_time": 338756.0,
      "text": "including substance use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 338780.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "depression and suicide."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 342220.0,
      "end_time": 345396.0,
      "text": "In our work with teens from LA Unified School District,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 345420.0,
      "end_time": 347636.0,
      "text": "we found that teens with sleep problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 347660.0,
      "end_time": 351860.0,
      "text": "were 55 percent more likely to have used alcohol in the past month."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 352900.0,
      "end_time": 356796.0,
      "text": "In another study with over 30,000 high school students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 356820.0,
      "end_time": 360396.0,
      "text": "they found that for each hour of lost sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 360420.0,
      "end_time": 364140.0,
      "text": "there was a 38 percent increase in feeling sad or hopeless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 365220.0,
      "end_time": 369100.0,
      "text": "and a 58 percent increase in teen suicide attempts."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 370420.0,
      "end_time": 372676.0,
      "text": "And if that&#39;s not enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 372700.0,
      "end_time": 375236.0,
      "text": "teens who skip out on sleep are at increased risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 379316.0,
      "text": "for a host of physical health problems that plague our country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 379340.0,
      "end_time": 383419.0,
      "text": "including obesity, heart disease and diabetes."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 384580.0,
      "end_time": 387476.0,
      "text": "Then there&#39;s the risk of putting a sleep-deprived teen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 387500.0,
      "end_time": 390360.0,
      "text": "with a newly minted driver&#39;s license,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390600.0,
      "end_time": 391340.0,
      "text": "behind the wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 391980.0,
      "end_time": 396476.0,
      "text": "Studies have shown that getting five hours or less of sleep per night"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 396500.0,
      "end_time": 402180.0,
      "text": "is the equivalent of driving with a blood alcohol content above the legal limit."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 408200.0,
      "end_time": 410515.0,
      "text": "Advocates of sleep-friendly start times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 410540.0,
      "end_time": 412596.0,
      "text": "and researchers in this area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 412620.0,
      "end_time": 414796.0,
      "text": "have produced tremendous science"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 414820.0,
      "end_time": 418716.0,
      "text": "showing the tremendous benefits of later start times."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 418740.0,
      "end_time": 421360.0,
      "text": "The findings are unequivocal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 421600.0,
      "end_time": 422756.0,
      "text": "and as a sleep scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 422780.0,
      "end_time": 425500.0,
      "text": "I rarely get to speak with that kind of certainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 426980.0,
      "end_time": 430796.0,
      "text": "Teens from districts with later start times get more sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 430820.0,
      "end_time": 434316.0,
      "text": "To the naysayers who may think that if schools start later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 434340.0,
      "end_time": 435979.0,
      "text": "teens will just stay up later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 436740.0,
      "end_time": 437996.0,
      "text": "the truth is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 438200.0,
      "end_time": 439955.0,
      "text": "their bedtimes stay the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 439980.0,
      "end_time": 442236.0,
      "text": "but their wake-up times get extended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444420.0,
      "text": "resulting in more sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 445180.0,
      "end_time": 447556.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re more likely to show up for school;"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 447580.0,
      "end_time": 451476.0,
      "text": "school absences dropped by 25 percent in one district."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 451500.0,
      "end_time": 454760.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re less likely to drop out."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 454100.0,
      "end_time": 457596.0,
      "text": "Not surprisingly, they do better academically."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 457620.0,
      "end_time": 462356.0,
      "text": "So this has real implications for reducing the achievement gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 462380.0,
      "end_time": 465760.0,
      "text": "Standardized test scores in math and reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 465100.0,
      "end_time": 467540.0,
      "text": "go up by two to three percentage points."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 468140.0,
      "end_time": 473716.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s as powerful as reducing class sizes by one-third fewer students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 473740.0,
      "end_time": 476916.0,
      "text": "or replacing a so-so teacher in the classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 476940.0,
      "end_time": 479100.0,
      "text": "with a truly outstanding one."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 482796.0,
      "text": "Their mental and physical health improves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 482820.0,
      "end_time": 485156.0,
      "text": "and even their families are happier."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 485180.0,
      "end_time": 489996.0,
      "text": "I mean, who wouldn&#39;t enjoy a little more pleasantness from our teens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490200.0,
      "end_time": 491979.0,
      "text": "and a little less crankiness?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 492860.0,
      "end_time": 494716.0,
      "text": "Even their communities are safer"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 494740.0,
      "end_time": 497276.0,
      "text": "because car crash rates go down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 497300.0,
      "end_time": 500140.0,
      "text": "a 70 percent reduction in one district."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 501220.0,
      "end_time": 503636.0,
      "text": "Given these tremendous benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 503660.0,
      "end_time": 504996.0,
      "text": "you might think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 505200.0,
      "end_time": 507716.0,
      "text": "well, this is a no-brainer, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 507740.0,
      "end_time": 512200.0,
      "text": "So why have we as a society failed to heed this call?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 513500.0,
      "end_time": 517590.0,
      "text": "Often the argument against later start times goes something like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 517820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520116.00000000006,
      "text": "\"Why should we delay start times for teenagers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 520140.0,
      "end_time": 523380.0,
      "text": "We need to toughen them up so they&#39;re ready for the real world!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 524200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526915.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s like saying to the parent of a two-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 526940.0,
      "end_time": 528436.0,
      "text": "\"Don&#39;t let Johnny nap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 528460.0,
      "end_time": 530876.0,
      "text": "or he won&#39;t be ready for kindergarten.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 530900.0,
      "end_time": 532100.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 533700.0,
      "end_time": 537596.0,
      "text": "Delaying start times also presents many logistical challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 537620.0,
      "end_time": 539996.0,
      "text": "Not just for students and their families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 540200.0,
      "end_time": 542396.0,
      "text": "but for communities as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 542420.0,
      "end_time": 543996.0,
      "text": "Updating bus routes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 544200.0,
      "end_time": 546760.0,
      "text": "increased transportation costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 546100.0,
      "end_time": 547636.0,
      "text": "impact on sports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 547660.0,
      "end_time": 550760.0,
      "text": "care before or after school."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 550100.0,
      "end_time": 554676.0,
      "text": "These are the same concerns that come up in district after district,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 554700.0,
      "end_time": 556676.0,
      "text": "time and again around the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 556700.0,
      "end_time": 558780.0,
      "text": "as school start times are debated."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 559780.0,
      "end_time": 561459.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re legitimate concerns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 562460.0,
      "end_time": 565340.0,
      "text": "but these are problems we have to work through."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 565940.0,
      "end_time": 568196.0,
      "text": "They are not valid excuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 568220.0,
      "end_time": 570980.0,
      "text": "for failing to do the right thing for our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 571740.0,
      "end_time": 576620.0,
      "text": "which is to start middle and high schools no earlier than 8:30am."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 577580.0,
      "end_time": 579476.0,
      "text": "And in districts around the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 579500.0,
      "end_time": 582116.0,
      "text": "big and small, who have made this change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 582140.0,
      "end_time": 585915.0,
      "text": "they found that these fears are often unfounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 585940.0,
      "end_time": 590356.0,
      "text": "and far outweighed by the tremendous benefits for student health"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 590380.0,
      "end_time": 592360.0,
      "text": "and performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 592600.0,
      "end_time": 594200.0,
      "text": "and our collective public safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 595980.0,
      "end_time": 597756.0,
      "text": "So tomorrow morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 597780.0,
      "end_time": 602500.0,
      "text": "when coincidentally we get to set our clocks back by an hour"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 603580.0,
      "end_time": 607900.0,
      "text": "and you get that delicious extra hour of sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 609100.0,
      "end_time": 611600.0,
      "text": "and the day seems a little longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 611900.0,
      "end_time": 613540.0,
      "text": "and a little more full of hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 614580.0,
      "end_time": 618500.0,
      "text": "think about the tremendous power of sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 619340.0,
      "end_time": 621916.0,
      "text": "And think about what a gift it would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 621940.0,
      "end_time": 625956.0,
      "text": "for our children to be able to wake up naturally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 625980.0,
      "end_time": 628220.0,
      "text": "in harmony with their own biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 629220.0,
      "end_time": 630476.0,
      "text": "Thank you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 630500.0,
      "end_time": 631700.0,
      "text": "and pleasant dreams."
    }
  ]
}